2-D Data Structure

Disclaimer about today's session

  • More about method of analysis than analysis itself

  • All of analysis can be done without dplyr

  • Coding is not only about input -> output

  • A good code should:

    • work
    • comprehensible (to your peers and yourself!)
      (logic can be followed - Spaghetti Code)
    • readable (not only by an expert in R)

Base R subsetting and sorting

## Subsetting
mtcars[c("Mazda RX4", "Mazda RX4 Wag"), c("mpg", "hp")]

## Sort 
mtcars[order(-mtcars$cyl, mtcars$mpg),]
